                        <td style="padding-top:20px;padding-left:30px;"> 
                            
                                 
                                    <b>Appointment Date and Time:</b>
                                    
                                    <apex:outputText value="{0,date,long}">
                                        <apex:param value="{!relatedTo.Appointment_Date__c}" />
                                    </apex:outputText> 
                                    {!relatedTo.Appointment_Time__c}
                                      <br/><br/>
                                      <b>Location:</b> {!relatedTo.Consultation_Type__c}
                                      <br/><br/>
                                      <b>Instructions:</b> 
                                      <br/>
                                      At the time of your appointment, simply open this link: <apex:outputLink value="{!relatedTo.Owner.Division}">{!relatedTo.Owner.Division}</apex:outputLink><br/><br/> 
                                      Your Energy Consultantâ€™s presentation will appear on your screen. <br/>
                                      You will receive a call from your Energy Consultant at this time to go over the presentation.
                                      <br/><br/>
                                      <b>You will be meeting with {!relatedTo.Account.Owner.Name}</b>
                                      <br/>
                                      <b>Phone:</b> {!relatedTo.Account.Owner.MobilePhone}
                                      <br/>
                                      <b>Email:</b> {!relatedTo.Account.Owner.email} 
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr style="vertical-align:top;">
                        <td style="padding-top:20px;padding-left:30px;"> 
                            <br/>
                            <b>Click <apex:outputLink value="http://sunpower.force.com/DesignSignOff/apex/MeetYourConsultant?id={!relatedTo.Owner.Id}"> here </apex:outputLink> to learn more about your Energy Consultant.</b>
                        </td>
                    </tr>
                    </table>
                    
                    
                    
                    <p style="margin-top:20px">To ensure the most effective use of your time please try to be at a computer to review the online proposal with your energy consultant.</p>
                    <p style="margin-top:20px">If you have any questions, please call me at the number below or reply back to this email.</p>
                    <br/><br/>
                    <p style="margin-top:20px">Sincerely, </p>
                    <br/>
                    <p style="margin-top:20px">
                        New Home Solar Advisors<br/>
                        <b>SunPower Corporation</b>
                        <br/>
                        <a href="www.sunpower.com">www.sunpower.com</a>
                    </p>
